Matching chiffon dupatta with embroidered four-sided border and intricate lace accents.

Off-white jacquard front-open shirt with a V-neckline featuring heart and flower-shaped tassels. Cotton culotte pants with tone-on-tone embroidery and cutwork to match the shirt.  Chiffon tie-dye dupatta in pinks, finished with a four-sided printed border and lace detailing that extends into the body.
